<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee6cfede-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s1039"><num value="1039">§ 1039.</num><heading> Time for filing purchase applications</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No application for the purchase of mineral interests under sections 1033 to 1039 of this title shall be filed until ninety days after <date date="1950-09-06">September 6, 1950</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee6cfedf-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1950-09-06/ch897/s7">Sept. 6, 1950, ch. 897, § 7</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/64/770">64 Stat. 770</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idee6cfee0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idee6cfee1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idee6cfee2-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was not enacted as part of the Bankhead-Jones Farm Tenant Act which constitutes a major part of this chapter.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
